SUMMARY:IMPROPMTU- LI - Eagle's Nest ride (25 R)-- RSVP required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide Leader: Bruce Black\
 n\nA ride to the west and north of Lititz with some rolling hills. The pac
 e will be between 14 and 16mph with multiple stop and regroup points. A 
 “short” stop for refreshment/coffee near the end of route at Zig's in 
 Lititz.\n\nThis ride is a social ride\, but cyclists are not expected to s
 tay in one group. Cyclists may pedal at their own comfortable paces. Pleas
 e be supportive of the other cyclists to avoid anyone biking alone or bein
 g dropped off the back of the last group.\n\nClick for [Ride with GPS](htt
 ps://ridewithgps.com/routes/54305292)\n\nHelmets are mandatory. No ear bud
 s. Please bring water and a basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, p
 ump/CO2 inflator).\n\nTo eliminate passing around a pen and paper waiver\,
  we require LBC Club membership and Meetup RSVP below to join this ride.\n
 \nBeing on Meetup does not mean you are a club member. [Join here](https:/
 /www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club_id=257148).\n\nYou
 r RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's [Code of Conduct](https://
 lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module
 _id=323984) \,\n[Rules of the Road](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/c
 ontent.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=325159) \, and [Ride Waive
 r](https://lancasterbikeclub.net/docs.ashx?id=454318)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/lancaster-bicycle-club/events/3140440
 33/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260330T211446Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260330T211446Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
