SUMMARY:Impromptu Free on Friday- GSV Pedal to Preserve 20 mile Route(20F)
  RSVP required
DESCRIPTION:Lancaster Bicycle Club (LBC) Meetup\nRide Leader: Rick Zook\nS
 weep: open\n\nAverage Pace 13-14 mph\nRide with GPS: [GSV Pedal to Preserv
 e 20 Mile Route (20F)](https://routes.lancasterbikeclub.net/cue/gsv-pedal-
 to-preserve-20-mile-route-20f/)\nOptional stop at [Fox Meadows Creamery](h
 ttps://www.foxmeadowscreamery.com/) halfway through route\,\ndepending on 
 what the group wants to do.\n\n**Please do not join this ride if you are n
 ot willing or able to stick with the group.** Ride leader will ride at the
  advertised average speed. This is intended to be a no-drop group ride. Th
 ere is sometimes\, but not always\, a sweep depending upon the size of the
  group.\n\nHelmets are mandatory\; please also plan to bring 1-2 water bot
 tles\, and basic repair kit (spare tube\, tire levers\, pump/CO2 inflator)
 .\nBeing a Meetup Member does not mean you are a club member. Use this [li
 nk to join](https://www.lancasterbikeclub.net/content.aspx?page_id=60&club
 _id=257148) the club.\nYour RSVP is your agreement to abide by the club's 
 [Code of Conduct](https://lancbikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_i
 d=22&club_id=257148&module_id=323984) and [Rules of the Road](https://lanc
 bikeclub.clubexpress.com/content.aspx?page_id=22&club_id=257148&module_id=
 325159)
